data.description: Beautiful 2 bedroom home, 1 bedroom is a suite and can be a 3rd bedroom. Crown molding throughout. Carrara marble floors in bathrooms. Brazilian cherry wood floors. Specially designed built-in entertainment center in living room. Beautiful chefs kitchen with Italian Granite counter tops and under cabinet lighting. Shelved laundry room off the kitchen. Two French doors from the master suite leading to a huge patio.  Lot size is 50 x 150. Driveway could fit 2 cars. New roof put on in 2022. Tuff shed in backyard.
